                                "type": "DESCRIPTION",
                                "data": {
                                    "text": [
                                        "The goal of this project was to create a complete brand identity for an imagined product. We identified a specific audience and presented a final product with three deliverables: a wordmark, business card, and physical product."
                                    ]
                                }
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "DESCRIPTION",
                                "data": {
                                    "text": [
                                        "The brand is named after the Silverpoint drawing technique, originating the in medieval times, where artists used silver wire in a stylus for markmaking on specially prepared paper."
                                    ]
                                }
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "sectionTitle": "process",
                "sectionTitleType": "level1",
